    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your observations of past orbital strikes have taught you how to coordinate small-arms fire in a similar fashion. Once per day as a full action you can designate a creature, object, or vehicle and call in a fire mission on that target. Allies you designate who are threatening that target in melee or wielding ranged weapons within the first two range increments of the target can make an attack roll against that target as a reaction. Activating this ability requires you to spend 1 Resolve Point for each ally who can make this attack.</p>"
